<p data-start="13267" data-end="13761">You’ll also want collectors for IIS (<code data-start="13304" data-end="13323">WebAdministration</code> → fallback <code data-start="13335" data-end="13370">appcmd.exe list site /config /xml</code>), Hyper-V (<code data-start="13382" data-end="13390">Get-VM</code> → fallback WMI <code data-start="13406" data-end="13427">root\virtualization</code>), Scheduled Tasks (<code data-start="13447" data-end="13466">Get-ScheduledTask</code> exists on 2012 R2), Local accounts (<code data-start="13503" data-end="13518">Get-LocalUser</code> is Win10+—fallback to <code data-start="13541" data-end="13551">net user</code> + WMI <code data-start="13558" data-end="13577">Win32_UserAccount</code>), Storage (<code data-start="13589" data-end="13599">Get-Disk</code> → fallback <code data-start="13611" data-end="13628">Win32_DiskDrive</code>, <code data-start="13630" data-end="13644">Win32_Volume</code>), Network (<code data-start="13656" data-end="13680">Get-NetIPConfiguration</code> → fallback <code data-start="13692" data-end="13707">ipconfig /all</code> + <code data-start="13710" data-end="13759">Get-WmiObject Win32_NetworkAdapterConfiguration</code>).</p>
