<h1 data-start="321" data-end="359">1) Introduce “Migration Units” (MUs)</h1>
<p data-start="360" data-end="442">Create a post-processing step that turns raw collector data into normalized units:</p>
<ul data-start="444" data-end="982">
<li data-start="444" data-end="520">
<p data-start="446" data-end="520"><strong data-start="446" data-end="454">DHCP</strong>: <code data-start="456" data-end="467">DhcpScope</code>, <code data-start="469" data-end="486">DhcpReservation</code>, <code data-start="488" data-end="500">DhcpOption</code>, <code data-start="502" data-end="520">DhcpFailoverPair</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="521" data-end="599">
<p data-start="523" data-end="599"><strong data-start="523" data-end="530">DNS</strong>: <code data-start="532" data-end="541">DnsZone</code> (type, DS-integrated, scavenging), <code data-start="577" data-end="599">ConditionalForwarder</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="600" data-end="674">
<p data-start="602" data-end="674"><strong data-start="602" data-end="609">IIS</strong>: <code data-start="611" data-end="620">IisSite</code>, <code data-start="622" data-end="634">IisAppPool</code>, <code data-start="636" data-end="648">IisBinding</code> (w/ SNI, cert thumbprint)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="675" data-end="718">
<p data-start="677" data-end="718"><strong data-start="677" data-end="688">Hyper-V</strong>: <code data-start="690" data-end="696">HvVm</code>, <code data-start="698" data-end="706">HvVhdx</code>, <code data-start="708" data-end="718">HvSwitch</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="719" data-end="776">
<p data-start="721" data-end="776"><strong data-start="721" data-end="728">SMB</strong>: <code data-start="730" data-end="740">SmbShare</code>, <code data-start="742" data-end="755">SmbAclEntry</code> (top-level snapshot)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="777" data-end="819">
<p data-start="779" data-end="819"><strong data-start="779" data-end="798">Storage/Network</strong>: <code data-start="800" data-end="808">Volume</code>, <code data-start="810" data-end="819">Adapter</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="820" data-end="904">
<p data-start="822" data-end="904"><strong data-start="822" data-end="840">Accounts/Tasks</strong>: <code data-start="842" data-end="853">LocalUser</code>, <code data-start="855" data-end="867">LocalGroup</code>, <code data-start="869" data-end="887">LocalGroupMember</code>, <code data-start="889" data-end="904">ScheduledTask</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="905" data-end="938">
<p data-start="907" data-end="938"><strong data-start="907" data-end="923">Certificates</strong>: <code data-start="925" data-end="938">Certificate</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="939" data-end="982">
<p data-start="941" data-end="982"><strong data-start="941" data-end="950">AD DS</strong>: <code data-start="952" data-end="970">DomainController</code>, <code data-start="972" data-end="982">FsmoRole</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
