<p data-start="2033" data-end="2045">quick notes:</p>
<ul data-start="2046" data-end="2609">
<li data-start="2046" data-end="2145">
<p data-start="2048" data-end="2145"><strong data-start="2048" data-end="2074">Invoke-ServerAudit.ps1</strong> (root) auto-locates the module and defaults <code data-start="2119" data-end="2128">-OutDir</code> to <code data-start="2132" data-end="2144">&lt;repo&gt;\out</code>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2146" data-end="2253">
<p data-start="2148" data-end="2253"><strong data-start="2148" data-end="2165">Migration.ps1</strong> builds Migration Units and evaluates readiness rules; results surface in HTML + <code data-start="2246" data-end="2252">csv/</code>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2254" data-end="2410">
<p data-start="2256" data-end="2410"><strong data-start="2256" data-end="2270">Report.ps1</strong> renders Bootstrap HTML and writes per-area CSVs (IIS, Hyper-V, SMB, Network, Storage, Local Accounts, Certs, Printers, plus MU &amp; findings).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2411" data-end="2541">
<p data-start="2413" data-end="2541"><strong data-start="2413" data-end="2444">rules/readiness.sample.json</strong> is optional; if you later add <code data-start="2475" data-end="2487">-RulesPath</code>, you can point to this for per-destination rulepacks.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2542" data-end="2609">
<p data-start="2544" data-end="2609"><strong data-start="2544" data-end="2553">tests</strong> cover core collectors; keep adding stubs as you extend.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2611" data-end="2690">want me to drop a <code data-start="2629" data-end="2641">.gitignore</code> and sample <code data-start="2653" data-end="2676">readiness.sample.json</code> contents too?</p>
